{"tid":1943102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"應承我 連哥可唔可以改吓個版面設計","createTime":"2020-03-25T12:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T13:20:31.000Z","uid":134997,"like":13,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0de60897ae72c144b81d5b1d46c6949cebb6c6c3","tid":1943102,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:38:41.000Z","msg":"老實講 我有小兒麻痹+電腦白痴 開cc台出嚟都有困難 我又唔識將cc台置頂<br />\n如果可以比我開app嘅時候直接問我想睇cc台（熱門）定其他po就好<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母 係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？<br />\n如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死<br />\n連我個淺藍老母都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應承我 唔可以當手足係condom？<br />\n我哋揸住佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 千祈唔可以中五毛分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可 煲底見！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789ace5c76b71e36dd863333fc876f4180fc63ce","tid":1943102,"uid":234509,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"睇錯達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd4991f4cb5b2b40f5fcaf294ca1a4939101e54","tid":1943102,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"789ace5c76b71e36dd863333fc876f4180fc63ce","tid":1943102,"uid":234509,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"睇錯達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:43:35.000Z","msg":"達哥 乜撚關係 我批要批你個羅"},{"pid":"36c568401405576016e600364dc997f47f5df480","tid":1943102,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"我匡智個淺藍上司都話有道理"},{"pid":"f25c80543428efc6582e781e0dcd300d6e704105","tid":1943102,"uid":